00:12:52,271 --> 00:12:54,607
Loki, tunggu!

211
00:12:55,983 --> 00:12:59,153
Hei! Anda pergi begitu cepat!

212
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:04,033
Awak tidak berterima kasih kepada Alvin
